cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.SD 

The paper discusses the challenges and solutions for mobile users to refind specific information previously found on the Web using a voice-controlled service accessible by telephone. This involves issues related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and software development (cs.SD).
